graph LR
    TrustyAIOp[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies
    TrustyAIOp -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes v1.19+]
    TrustyAIOp -.->|optional| OpenShift[OpenShift v4.6+]
    TrustyAIOp -.->|optional| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    TrustyAIOp -.->|optional| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrustyAIOp -->|watches/patches CRDs| KServe[KServe]
    TrustyAIOp -->|deploys| TrustyAIService[TrustyAI Service]
    TrustyAIOp -->|sidecar container| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy]
    TrustyAIOp -.->|ConfigMap injection| TrustedCA[ODH Trusted CA Bundle]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| TrustyAIOp
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving] -->|payload processing| TrustyAIService
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|metrics collection| TrustyAIService
    OpenShiftRouter[OpenShift Router] -->|external access| TrustyAIService

    %% External Services
    TrustyAIService -.->|DATABASE mode| ExtDB[External Database<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL]
    TrustyAIService -.->|PVC mode| PV[Persistent Volumes]

    %% API Server
    TrustyAIOp -->|control plane ops| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    K8s -->|provides| K8sAPI

    %% Service Mesh (implicit)
    OpenShift -.->|provides| OpenShiftRouter
    OpenShift -.->|provides| OAuthProxy

    %% Styling
    style TrustyAIOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenShift fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PrometheusOp fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TrustyAIService fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TrustedCA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenShiftRouter fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ExtDB fill:#f8e71c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PV fill:#f8e71c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

